script.name: plugin.roverview.compilelist
script.description: Resource Overview: Compile list of wares
script.sourceplaintext:
$data = table alloc
$table.wares.obj = table alloc $table.wares = table alloc $table.ship.wares = table alloc $table.station.wares = table alloc $table.ship.count = table alloc $table.station.count = table alloc $table.asterods = table alloc $table.stations = table alloc $data['wares'] = $table.wares $data['ship.wares'] = $table.ship.wares $data['station.wares'] = $table.station.wares $data['ware.objs'] = $table.wares.obj $data['ship.count'] = $table.ship.count $data['station.count'] = $table.station.count $data['asteroids'] = $table.asterods $data['factories'] = $table.stations
$objs = get ship array: of race Player class/type=Moveable Ship gosub sub.DoObjectList $objs = get station array: of race Player class/type=null gosub sub.DoObjectList
gosub sub.FindAsteroids gosub sub.GetProduction
* =================================== return $data
* ===================================
* ====================== * ====================== sub.DoObjectList: $i = size of array $objs while $i dec $i = $o = $objs[$i] gosub sub.DoObject end endsub
* ====================== * ====================== sub.DoObject: $wares = null if $o -> is of class Ship $table.obj = $table.ship.wares $table.obj.count = $table.ship.count $wares = $o ->get ship tradeable ware table: include hardware=[FALSE] else if $o -> is of class Station $complex.hangar = $o ->get complex hangar do if $complex.hangar -> exists endsub if $o -> is of class Factory skip if $o -> is of class Shipyard $table.stations[$o] = [TRUE] end $table.obj = $table.station.wares $table.obj.count = $table.station.count $wares = $o ->get station tradeable ware table end
if $wares $ware = get next key: table=$wares key=null while $ware $qty = $wares[$ware] gosub sub.DoWare $ware = get next key: table=$wares key=$ware end end endsub
* ====================== * ====================== sub.DoWare: if $qty > 0 $do.table = $table.wares gosub sub.AddTable $do.table = $table.obj gosub sub.AddTable $table = $table.wares.obj[$ware] if not $table $table = table alloc $table.wares.obj[$ware] = $table end $table[$o] = $qty $qty = 1 $do.table = $table.obj.count gosub sub.AddTable end endsub
* ====================== * ====================== sub.AddTable: $sub.val = $do.table[$ware] skip if $sub.val $sub.val = 0 $sub.val = $sub.val + $qty $do.table[$ware] = $sub.val endsub
* ====================== * ====================== sub.FindAsteroids: $x = get max sectors in x direction while $x dec $x = $y = get max sectors in y direction while $y dec $y = $sector = get sector from universe index: x=$x, y=$y skip if $sector -> exists continue $asteroids = $sector ->get asteroid table from sector skip if $asteroids continue
$key = get next key: table=$asteroids key=null while $key if $key -> is known if $key -> is asteroid scanned $yield = $key -> get asteroid yield $table.asterods[$key] = $yield end end $key = get next key: table=$asteroids key=$key end end end endsub
* ====================== * ====================== sub.GetProduction: $sector = [PLAYERSHIP] -> get sector @ $production.data = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.getdata : Sector=$sector Station Table=null Asteroid Table=null Existing Table=$table.stations Cycle Time=43200 $data['production'] = $production.data $cycle.time = $production.data[0]
$key = get next key: table=$table.stations key=null while $key $table = table alloc $table[$key] = [TRUE] @ $production.data = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.getdata : Sector=$sector Station Table=null Asteroid Table=null Existing Table=$table Cycle Time=$cycle.time $data[$key] = $production.data $key = get next key: table=$table.stations key=$key end endsub
* ====================== return null
